Melt Spread in large nonstick skillet over medium-high heat and cook chicken and onion, stirring frequently, until chicken is thoroughly cooked, about 4 minutes. Remove and set aside. Prepare Knorr(R) Rice Sides(TM) - Creamy Chicken flavor in same skillet according to package directions, stirring in broccoli during the last 5 minutes of cook time. Stir in chicken and onion. Sprinkle with bacon.